data.description: The impressive home features an open floor plan and exapansive living areas. Complete with a flow-through living/dining area and large windows. A foodie's dream, this spacious kitchen includes stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, a large island, beautifully maintained cabinetry, recessed lighting, pantry and built in microwave. Natural lighting creates the perfect ambiance in the king-sized main bedroom that boasts an ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. Main bathroom has a double vanity and standup shower. Host a bbq in the covered outdoor patio. A rare opportunity. Call to schedule a showing.
